<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nuoi simlei ah thepna leh gitlohna hai puona,
 Ni chengin thepin I um zing ui;
 Ka mitmuh leh bila ka zakhaw hin,
 Gitloh ah ei tun.

[V2]
 Mahleh Ka Lapa hehpihna lopi chun,
 Sihlung hei A ngaidam;
 Sihlung hei in ka hung ie Lalpa (2)
 Ka gitloh ngaidam in.

[V3]
 2. A hehpihna vangin chang bang damin I um ui,
 Mahleh A hehpih I haih zing ui;
 Kalvari a tatna ngailo bangin,
 Lei pak ka na lawp.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel hawihna cheng cheng hi kumsawt a ting
 Mahleh a hawihna I hawl zing ui; [zo puoi,
 Khawvel a hin nun nuomin leng mahleng,
 Vak mang ka na hi .

[V5]
 4. Beimangte hawla hukdam dingin Lalpa Isu'n,
 Hehpih in ei hawl gimthei chate;
 Gitloh thihna thima kimang cheng cheng
 Te tho kit hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>Sihlung Hei A Ngaidam</title>
<hymn_number>144</hymn_number>
<author>Tawia</author>
</song>